column2: SELECT up_id,  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) as objId   FROM #upload  WHERE  dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) IS NOT NULL  SELECT TOP #   p.ra,p.dec, p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj,ISNULL(s.z,#) as redshift,ISNULL(s.z_noqso,#) as z_noqso,ISNULL(s.z_person,#) as z_person,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as redshiftErr,ISNULL(s.zErr_noqso,#) as zErr_noqso,ISNULL(s.zOffset,#) as zOffset,ISNULL(s.zWarning,#) as zWarning  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
